cpu

Class MultilevelQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • cpu.Scheduler
      • cpu.MultilevelQueue

  • public class MultilevelQueue
extends Scheduler
    The Class MultilevelQueue that encapsulates algorithm which uses 2 queues: RR as the foreground and FCFS as the background. In this case the foreground queue (RR) has absolute priority over the background queue (FCFS).
